sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant UI as Dashboard
    participant API
    participant RM as RuntimeManager
    participant Pty as PtyRuntime
    participant Reg as SessionRegistry
    participant Claude

    User->>UI: Click "New session"
    UI->>API: POST /api/runtime-sessions { persistence: "ephemeral" }
    API->>RM: create(request)
    RM->>Pty: create()
    Pty->>Claude: spawn claude via node-pty
    Pty-->>RM: RuntimeRef
    RM->>Reg: save RuntimeSessionRecord
    RM-->>API: RuntimeRef
    API-->>UI: sessionId
    UI->>API: WebSocket attach
